title: Crawlthe.net webcrawler client
description:
Together we crawl the net. This web crawler does not use a big server to crawl websites. It crowd sources this process.
Everyone can help crawl the net with downloading the client and pressing start.
And everyone can get unlimited websites indexed, crawled and listet for free on CrawlTheNet. You just have to add your link to the crawling queue and the website will be crawled. Or just wait until the crawler finds the website by itself. Of course this takes time depending on how many people are helping to crawl the net
